On PC side
 - roscore

Startup turtlebot
  - ssh hpsta@<turtlebot ip>
    password: turtle2023
    once logged in, run:
  - ./startup_robot.sh <ip of PC>

On PC side
    to start up rviz, run
  - roslaunch turtlebot3_bringup turtlebot3_remote.launch
  - rosrun rviz rviz -d `rospack find turtlebot3_automatic_parking`/rviz/turtlebot3_automatic_parking.rviz
  
    to record a log
  - cd $HOME/src/hpsta/hpsta_turtlebot/hpsta_demo_ros1_image
  - python3 record-log.py <optional log name>
        
    run the parking demo
  - roslaunch turtlebot3_automatic_parking turtlebot3_automatic_parking.launch        
